>> Rik van Riel wrote:
>>
>>> MADV_DONTNEED, unpatched, 1000 loops
>>>
>>> real    0m13.672s
>>> user    0m1.217s
>>> sys     0m45.712s
>>>
>>>
>>> MADV_DONTNEED, with patch, 1000 loops
>>>
